title: Week 1 Matchups + Zeke Tilt, Tony Tony! - Fantasy Football Podcast for 9/10
description:
The Fantasy Footballers are back with a new episode with Week 1 underway! On today’s fantasy football podcast, lots of Week 1 matchup breakdowns. Plus, injury updates, a recap of the Cowboys vs Buccaneers season opener, and the debut of “Fantasy Faceoff”! Manage your redraft, keeper, and dynasty fantasy football teams with the #1 fantasy football podcast. -- Fantasy Football Podcast for September 10th, 2021
  
 (06:25) - FootClan Friday
 (06:25) - NFL News
 (18:20) - Fantasy Forecast
 (18:50) - Chargers at Washington
 (22:05) - Jets at Panthers
 (30:20) - Jaguars at Texans
 (34:20) - Browns at Chiefs
 (40:50) - Dolphins at Patriots
 (44:25) - Packers at Saints
 (49:05) - Broncos at Giants
 (53:45) - Bears at Rams
 (55:30) - Ravens at Raiders
 (59:50) - Fantasy Faceoff
